<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE topic PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA 1.2 Topic//EN" "/SysSchema/dita/dtd/technicalContent/dtd/topic.dtd">
<topic xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" base="Princeton" id="Sys_Diag_FW_Img_Up" xml:lang="en-US">
  <title>Firmware Image Upload (subcommand opcode
  0x02)</title>

  <body>
    <p>Use the Upload Firmware Image command to upload the
    firmware image from the specified firmware slot to the host.</p>

    <fig id="NVM_Express_Vendor_Specific_Command_Firm_6bht97qqbz">
      <title>NVM Express Vendor Specific Command
      Firmware Image Upload Control Flow</title>

      <image href="Graphics/Admin Command Manager/System_Diag_FW_Upload.svg" placement="break" width="5.5in"/>
    </fig>

    <table id="_6cht97qqbz">
      <title>NVM Express Vendor Specific Command
      Firmware Image Upload Control Flow</title>

      <tgroup cols="3">
        <colspec colname="c1" colwidth=".5in"/>

        <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.5in"/>

        <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="4in"/>

        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>No.</entry>

            <entry>Message</entry>

            <entry>Description</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">1</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">CmdReady64</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The command is
            received by one of the Data Managers.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">2</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">CmdReady</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Data
            Manager forwards the command to the Admin Command Manager for
            processing.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">3</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">FwUpdtReq</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Admin
            Command Manager sends a request to the Control Manager to upload
            the firmware image from a specified firmware slot to the
            controller memory.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">4</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">FlashRead</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Control
            Manager issues flash read requests.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">5</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">FlashOpCpl</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Flash
            Interface responds to the flash read requests.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">6</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">FwUpdtCpl</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Control
            Manager sends a firmware update completion request to the Admin
            Command Manager.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">7</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">EgressDMA</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Admin
            Command Manager issues Egress DMA requests to transfer the
            firmware image to the host.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">8</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">DMACpl</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The DMA engine
            responds with DMA completion messages.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">9</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">CplQueueUpdate</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Admin
            Command Manager sends a completion queue update request to the
            Completion Manager.</p></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">10</b> </p></entry>

            <entry><p> <b otherprops="bold">CplQueueUpdateCpl</b>
            </p></entry>

            <entry><p>The Completion
            Manager replies back to the Admin Command Manager when the
            completion has been successfully sent to the host.</p></entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
  </body>
</topic>